Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "korisno" in different forms and positions:

1. *Korisno* je učiti strane jezike. (It's useful to learn foreign languages.)
2. Sve što si mi rekao bilo je *korisno*. (Everything you told me was useful.)
3. Napisala sam *korisnu* belešku za sastanak. (I wrote a useful note for the meeting.)
4. Ukoliko želite da ostvarite svoje ciljeve, *korisno* je da napravite plan. (If you want to achieve your goals, it's useful to make a plan.)
5. *Korisnije* bi bilo da se usredsredite na svoj posao. (It would be more useful to focus on your job.)
6. *Najkorisnije* stvari u životu su besplatne. (The most useful things in life are free.)
7. Nudimo vam *korisne* informacije o našim proizvodima. (We offer you useful information about our products.)
8. Drago mi je što sam mogla biti *korisna*. (I'm glad I could be helpful.)
9. Ova knjiga je *korisna* za studente prava. (This book is useful for law students.)
10. Upišite se na *korisni* kurs računovodstva. (Enroll in a useful accounting course.)

Note: The star (*) indicates the word "korisno" in the sentence.